text: Cymatonycha meridionalis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 1995. It is known from Colombia and Venezuela.BioLib.cz - Cymatonycha meridionalis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1995
